import React from 'react'; import '../styles/Controls.css'; function Controls({ params, onParamChange, isPaused, onTogglePause, onDownloadSVG }) { const handleChange = (e) => { const { name, value } = e.target; const numValue = parseFloat(value); onParamChange(name, numValue); }; return (
{params.separation.toFixed(1)}
{params.alignment.toFixed(1)}
{params.cohesion.toFixed(1)}
{params.trailLength}
{params.colorRandomness}%
{params.simulationSpeed.toFixed(1)}x
{params.newAgents}
); } export default Controls;
